		"Name": "Hyperion",
		"Details": "A purely experimental weapons platform, the Hyperion Superheavy BattleMech was designed in concert by a number of members of various Clan scientist castes. Somehow, using the cutting edge science available to them, the Clan scientists managed to produce a viable superheavy chassis, the first since the Matar centuries before. After extensive testing, the Clans decided to develop the Hyperion as an OmniMech capable of exceeding the famous Dire Wolf in speed, armor, and firepower. Built on a 375-rated XL engine, with an Endo-Steel Framework with 18.5 tons of Ferro-Fibrous armor, the Hyperion Omni boasts a staggering 72.5 tons of free tonnage for weaponry and equipment. The A configuration of the Hyperion is a brutal, close range brawler. A staggering four UAC/20s, each fed by two tons of ammo pound anything that wanders into range into dust. A single ER Large laser is its sole concession to long ranged combat. \n\n <b><color=#e51717>COMMUNITY CONTENT</color></b>",
